            <h1 style="float: left;"><b>ICE Continues to Transfer Detainees Between Facilities, as Covid-19 Cases Spike
                    in Detention Centers</b></h1>
            <p style="text-align: center; float: right; padding-top: 10px;">
            <span class="hcdagheader" style="display: inline-block; padding: 10px;">Compiled by <b>Human Rights First and the Harvard 
                College Data Analytics Group</b></span></p>
        </div>
    </div>

